- move this to an webserver (with php)
- download Sencha Touch http://www.sencha.com/products/touch/
- rename the whole senchat touch download folder to "sencha-touch" and move it to your root directory
- create an "media" folder in the root directory of your webserver and put some iPad ready mp4s into it
- rename config.sample.inc.php to config.inc.php and configure it
- fire up index.html on your iPad
- see the very first roots of an lovely Media Center based uppon Sencha Touch Kitchensink example
- see how nothing happends at all, because this is just a very early not even prototype release
- help to create the wonderfull world of tomorrow.